  "detailed_description": "Welcome to HeliVR Simulator, an immersive virtual reality helicopter flying simulation experience designed for both novice and experienced players.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n• VR Cockpit with extreme realism and attention to detail<br />\r\n• All cockpit instruments function exactly as they would in real life.<br />\r\n• Experience realistic simulated aircraft behavior across various scenarios.<br />\r\n• Four carefully crafted worlds to explore, from small to large<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHeliVR Simulator is developed by aviation enthusiasts who accepted the challenge of bringing the best VR experience to life for all kinds of players!",
